   Directions to CERC and Columbia Community Profile  [btrfly.gif]

      Road Map from St. Louis, Kansas City, or Jefferson City to CERC

      From Lambert St. Louis International Airport: Starting at Lambert-St.
      Louis International, begin on Interstate 70 heading West for
      approximately 110 miles. Turn South (left) on US HWY 63 and proceed for
      approximately 3 miles to the Columbia AC exit. Turn East (left) onto
      New Haven Road and proceed approximately 1 mile to CERC at 4200 New
      Haven Rd.

      From the Kansas City International Airport: Starting at the Kansas City
      International Airport, take Interstate 435 South to Interstate 70 East.
      Follow I-70 East for approximately 120 miles to US HWY 63 South
      (right). Follow US HWY 63 South for approximately 3 miles to the
      Columbia AC exit. Turn East (left) onto New Haven Road and proceed
      approximately 1 mile to CERC at 4200 New Haven Rd.

      From the Columbia Regional Airport: Take the airport access road North
      to State Road H. Turn left onto State Road H and proceed to US HWY 63.
      Turn right (North) onto HWY 63 and proceed to the Columbia AC exit,
      approximately 7.5 miles. Turn Right (East) onto AC (New Haven Road) and
      proceed approximately 1 mile to CERC at 4200 New Haven Rd.

